reviewText: A little bit different than what I usually like but it is OK

In spite of what you see on the cover this is not a damsel in distress bondage video but instead a porno from what appears to be from the late seventies early or mid eighties circa a very cheap move by this company to deceive its customers with such misleading box art truly not what you would expect because the women in this video are neither damsels nor do they appear to be distressed and they're certainly not bound and gagged.
